"D:\Halo\Eldewrito\Game\maps\tags.dat"

CreateModPackage
No Friction
Waterslide time! Removes friction for all materials, physics models, bipeds, and vehicles (save for anti gravity vehicles which ignore the laws)
Newbie
1.0
Multiplayer

## All materials
ForEach matg ForEach Materials SetField Friction 0
## ForEach matg ForEach PlayerInformation SetField AirborneAcceleration 0
## depending on this value you either have lots of control, but act like you have lots of friction, or you have no control but now can slide just as easily 
## as all other objects

## All physics models
ForEach phmo ForEach Spheres SetField Friction 0
ForEach phmo ForEach Pills SetField Friction 0
ForEach phmo ForEach Boxes SetField Friction 0
ForEach phmo ForEach Triangles SetField Friction 0
ForEach phmo ForEach Polyhedra SetField Friction 0

## All biped
ForEach bipd SetField BipedGroundPhysics.RuntimeMinimumNormalK 0.9975

## All vehicles
ForEach vehi SetField HavokVehiclePhysics.GroundMaximumSlope1 1
ForEach vehi ForEach HavokVehiclePhysics.AntiGravityPoints SetField AntigravNormalK0 1
ForEach vehi ForEach Seats SetField FlippedEvictionTime 32000
## ForEach vehi SetField VehicleFlags EnableWheeliePoppingHack

SaveModPackage
ExitModPackage
Quit